title: S2 E10: Gus' Dad May Have Killed an Old Guy with Dan Miller
description:
This week, Maggie & Tim are joined by their close friend and crew member Dan Miller to talk about Season 2 Episode 10: Gus' Dad May Have Killed an Old Guy.
They talk about the episode, their favorite memories, answer some incredible fan questions and Dan reveals he, too, was a part of the Tim Broken Collarbone Snafu!
